Jaate-jaate ek baar recap karlo:

VS Code mein Counter wala code likhna hai.

Usme useEffect daalna hai jo har click par console mein message dikhaye.

Ek baar Greeting component bana kar use App.js mein multiple times call karna hai.

hw-2

Input Box banao: Jisme user apna naam likh sake.

Display Name: Niche ek <h2> mein wahi naam dikhe jo type ho raha hai.

Magic Button: Ek button banao "Lock Name". Jab user click kare, toh input box gayab ho jaye aur sirf naam dikhe.

Conditional Styling: Agar naam 10 characters se zyada lamba ho jaye, toh uska color Red ho jaye (Hint: style={{ color: name.length > 10 ? 'red' : 'black' }}).